What's happening?

8
00:01:39,620 --> 00:01:40,500
What is that?

9
00:01:59,460 --> 00:02:01,980
Help me!

10
00:02:01,980 --> 00:02:02,660
Hold on!

11
00:02:31,100 --> 00:02:32,660
Faster! They're gaining on us!

12
00:02:32,820 --> 00:02:33,940
I'm driving a car,

13
00:02:33,940 --> 00:02:34,580
princess,

14
00:02:34,580 --> 00:02:35,660
not a jet.

15
00:02:38,100 --> 00:02:39,340
Steady, nice and steady.

16
