♪I'll fight until I bend♪

18
00:02:56,120 --> 00:03:00,400
♪Though fate may choke me tight♪

19
00:03:00,720 --> 00:03:04,600
♪Call my name,
and I'll follow you into the night♪

20
00:03:04,880 --> 00:03:08,970
♪Don't care if the answer's in sight♪

21
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:14,000
♪Facing fate, we'll stand side by side♪

22
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:22,400
♪Through thorns,
we charge to the rescue♪

23
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:24,140
♪Those unknown adventures and schemes♪

24
00:03:24,140 --> 00:03:24,660
Wait.

25
