Where's the clam?

26
00:03:25,980 --> 00:03:26,700
It's gone.

27
00:03:28,020 --> 00:03:28,860
Vanished.

28
00:03:28,860 --> 00:03:31,640
♪Will ultimately be conquered in time♪

29
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:36,600
♪Through raging flames we'll fight♪

30
00:03:36,880 --> 00:03:38,780
♪Beyond the nightmares
we'll stand in the light♪

31
00:03:38,780 --> 00:03:39,460
Get in the car!

32
